      <title>韩国 4 月份消费者通胀率降至 2.9%</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korea-april-inflation-29-yy-lower-than-expected-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四官方数据显示，韩国四月份消费者通胀三个月来首次放缓，低于经济学家的预期，支撑了市场对下半年货币宽松的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korea-april-inflation-29-yy-lower-than-expected-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 23:10:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Woolworths 提醒顾客在销售放缓和生活成本下降的情况下保持谨慎</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/australian-retailer-woolworths-third-quarter-sales-rise-28-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚 Woolworths 周四警告说，尽管通胀有所缓和，但消费者仍然保持谨慎态度，生活成本面临压力，因为这家超市运营商面临着其最大的业务——澳大利亚食品的销售放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/australian-retailer-woolworths-third-quarter-sales-rise-28-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 22:49:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>第一季度业绩好于预期 星展银行预计今年净利润将上升</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/singapore-bank-dbs-first-quarter-net-profit-rises-15-year-record-high-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡最大银行星展集团周四表示，在总收入强劲增长的推动下，第一季度净利润增长 15%，超出预期，预计今年净利润将从 2023 年开始增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/singapore-bank-dbs-first-quarter-net-profit-rises-15-year-record-high-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 22:39:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>赌场运营商米高梅第一季度澳门业务强劲超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/casino-operator-mgm-beats-first-quarter-estimates-strength-macau-business-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[米高梅国际酒店集团 (MGM Resorts International) 周三第一季度业绩超出了华尔街预期，这得益于其中国业务的强劲发展，赌场运营商继续受益于疫情后入境限制的放松。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/casino-operator-mgm-beats-first-quarter-estimates-strength-macau-business-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 22:38:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳洲银行NAB现金利润下降13% 回购9.79亿美元股票</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/national-australia-bank-first-half-cash-earnings-fall-13-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚国民银行周四公布，由于面临高昂的运营成本和激烈的竞争，其上半年现金收益下降了约 13%，但将正在进行的股票回购计划增加了 15 亿澳元（9.79 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/national-australia-bank-first-half-cash-earnings-fall-13-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 22:10:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
